      <h2>How We Approach Litigation</h2>
      <div class="content">
        <p>
          Litigation strategy starts before a complaint is filed. We identify the governing documents, the most important facts,
          the pressure points, and the fastest path to a durable outcome. If the matter belongs in court, we build the record early.
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Early case assessment and strategy memo (what matters, what doesn’t, and why).</li>
          <li>Document and timeline organization to support negotiation or filing.</li>
          <li>Demand letter strategy aligned with your leverage and goals.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
